those licenses.

================================================================
LAYER 2 — THE CURATION
================================================================

The selection of which images to include, the 20-category taxonomy
(`abstract/`, `architecture/`, `cafe/`, `fashion/`, ... ), the directory
structure used to map engine prompts to image candidates, and any
metadata or organizing artifacts in this repository (this LICENSE file,
the README, naming conventions, structural choices) are:

    Copyright © Lokuma. All rights reserved.

The curation is published here so the Lokuma Design Engine
(https://github.com/Mumu090909/lokuma-design-engine) has a deterministic
fallback image dataset. It is NOT licensed for:

  - Redistribution as a "stock image pack" or curated dataset.
  - Use as the fallback dataset of a different image generator,
    website builder, design tool, or any competing product.
  - Any commercial reuse of the curation, taxonomy, or structure.
  - Republication under a different name with the curation intact.

Mirroring this repository for the sole purpose of running an unmodified
Lokuma Design Engine is permitted.

For any other use of the curation, contact Lokuma for written permission.

